ai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363430/extras/f4889559787dd6752bf63a3f874f476a.mp4?t=1706151794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li>Focus your spirit to learn new spells and evolve your Spellbook.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363430/extras/2c2f04ade17a9e35f1366afa1022738d.gif?t=1706151794\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2363430/extras/2c2f04ade17a9e35f1366afa1022738d.poster.avif?t=1706151794\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span><br><br>Progress is made solely trough spells which change combat dynamics and are cruicial in order to advance.</li></ul><br>Note this game is a Card Battler with a Adventure part. <br>It's not a conventional RPG.",
